    <div class="about">
        <h1>About Quora Lite</h1>

        <p>
            Quora Lite is a simple platform where users can share their thoughts, ideas, and experiences.
            It is inspired by real-world social platforms but built with simplicity and learning in mind.
        </p>

        <p>
            This project demonstrates full-stack development using technologies like Node.js, Express,
            and EJS. It allows users to create, view, edit, and delete posts easily.
        </p>

        <p>
            The goal of this project is to understand how modern web applications work behind the scenes
            while keeping the user interface clean and minimal.
        </p>

